text.textblock: This notice of receipt of applications for modification of exemptions and for party to an exemption is published in accordance with part 107 of the Hazardous Materials Transportations Act (49 U.S.C. 1806; 49 CFR 1.53(e)).
Issued in Washington, DC, on January 12, 1994.

signjob.textblock: Chief, Exemption Programs, Office of Hazardous Materials Exemptions and Approvals.
